---
import LightLayout from '../layouts/LightLayout.astro';
---

<LightLayout title="ACAS Cheatsheet — Raquel" description="Guion práctico para la primera llamada del conciliator de ACAS. Referencia R194247/26.">

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-12 md:pt-20 pb-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <span class="text-5xl">📞</span>
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">ACAS Cheatsheet</h1>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider" style="background: var(--color-primary-soft); color: var(--color-primary);">R194247/26</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-medium mt-1" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Para Raquel · primera llamada conciliator</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl p-5 mb-6" style="background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fcd34d;">
      <p class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: #92400e;">🎯 Regla de oro</p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #78350f;">
        Esta llamada <strong>no es una negociación</strong>. Es solo una introducción donde el conciliator se presenta y empieza a entender tu caso. <strong>No tienes que aceptar nada</strong>, ni dar cifras, ni comprometerte a nada. Si te presionan, di: <em>"prefiero pensarlo y volver con mi respuesta por email"</em>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">Antes de coger el teléfono</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-cloud);">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">✅ Ten a mano</p>
        <ul class="text-sm space-y-1 list-disc pl-5" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
          <li>Tu referencia: <strong>R194247/26</strong></li>
          <li>Esta página abierta en el móvil</li>
          <li>Bolígrafo y papel para apuntar el nombre del conciliator, su email y número directo</li>
          <li>Un sitio tranquilo, sin niños cerca, donde puedas hablar 15-20 min</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-cloud);">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">📵 Si te pilla mal el momento</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
          Totalmente legítimo decir: <em>"This isn't a good time, can we book a call for [día/hora]?"</em>. No pasa nada. Es mejor llamar tú con cabeza fría que contestar en caliente.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">Apertura · cómo te presentas</h2>
    <div class="rounded-xl p-5" style="background: var(--color-primary-soft); border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2);">
      <p class="text-sm italic leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">
        "Hi, thank you for calling. Yes, I'd prefer this call to be in English, though I may take a moment to think before answering some questions. I want to be careful with my words on a matter this important. Could you start by telling me your name, your direct email, and how the process will work from here?"
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs mt-2" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
      Esto consigue tres cosas: (1) marcas que el inglés no es tu lengua materna sin victimizarte, (2) te das permiso a pensar antes de responder, (3) le pasas la pelota a ellos para que hablen primero.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">Tu caso en 60 segundos</h2>
    <p class="text-sm mb-3" style="color: var(--color-stone);">Si te pide que le cuentes qué pasó, esta es la versión corta. Apréndetela.</p>
    <div class="rounded-xl p-5" style="background: var(--color-cloud); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);">
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">
        "I worked at the Maidenhead M&S store as a stylist from 2013 until I had to resign on 3rd May 2026, after thirteen years."
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">
        "For more than three years I worked Monday to Friday, which had become my established pattern. In early 2026 the store began pressuring me to work weekends, which I cannot do because of my childcare responsibilities."
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">
        "I raised my concerns and submitted a flexible working request, but the pressure continued. The stress made me unwell and my GP signed me off with work-related anxiety."
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">
        "When I came back, nothing had changed. I felt I had no realistic option but to resign. I believe this amounts to constructive dismissal and indirect sex discrimination, because the requirement disadvantages women with primary childcare responsibilities."
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs mt-2" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
      4 párrafos, ~90 segundos hablado despacio. Si te interrumpe con preguntas, perfecto, contesta y vuelves al hilo cuando puedas.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">Lo que SÍ puedes decir</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: #065f46;">✅ Estás abierta a settlement</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #047857;">
          <em>"I'm open to reaching a settlement that reflects the seriousness of what happened."</em> Esto le dice al conciliator que vale la pena trabajar el caso.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: #065f46;">✅ M&S ya respondió</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #047857;">
          <em>"M&S responded to our without prejudice letter on 11th May through Jo Wolski, denying liability but agreeing to engage through ACAS."</em>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: #065f46;">✅ Tienes asesoramiento</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #047857;">
          <em>"I'm being advised on this matter, so I prefer to confirm anything substantive in writing before agreeing."</em> Esto te da margen para consultar antes de responder.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: #ecfdf5; border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: #065f46;">✅ Preferencia de email</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #047857;">
          <em>"Going forward, could we keep most of our communication by email? It helps me make sure I understand everything precisely."</em>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">Lo que NO debes decir</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca;">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: #991b1b;">❌ Nunca des una cifra</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #b91c1c;">
          Si te pregunta <em>"how much are you looking for?"</em>, NO contestes con un número. Di: <em>"I'd rather discuss figures once I've understood M&S's position. What have they indicated?"</em> Devuelve la pregunta.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca;">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: #991b1b;">❌ Nada sobre tu nuevo trabajo</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #b91c1c;">
          No menciones The Home Staging Team por iniciativa propia. Si te pregunta <em>"are you working now?"</em>, di: <em>"I'm taking time to recover and exploring my options."</em> Y nada más.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca;">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: #991b1b;">❌ No insultes ni emocionales fuertes</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #b91c1c;">
          Aunque tengas razón al estar enfadada, mantén tono profesional. El conciliator habla con M&S después; cualquier dramatismo se transmite y baja tu credibilidad.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca;">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: #991b1b;">❌ No aceptes nada en la llamada</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #b91c1c;">
          Si te dice <em>"M&S has offered X, do you accept?"</em>, di: <em>"Thank you, please put that in writing and I'll consider it carefully."</em> Nunca aceptes en directo.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca;">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: #991b1b;">❌ No firmes nada sin solicitor</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: #b91c1c;">
          Un settlement agreement requiere asesoramiento legal independiente para ser válido (s.203 ERA). Si llegamos ahí, contratamos solicitor de 1h (£350-750, recuperable de M&S).
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">Preguntas que probablemente te haga</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3">

      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-cloud);">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">¿"How would you like to resolve this?"</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
          <em>"I'm looking for a fair financial settlement that reflects the loss of a thirteen-year career, plus an agreed reference. I'm willing to listen to what M&S proposes."</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-cloud);">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">¿"Are you open to returning to work?"</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
          <em>"After everything that's happened, including being signed off with work-related anxiety, returning is not realistic. Trust and confidence have broken down."</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-cloud);">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">¿"Have you found new employment?"</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
          <em>"I'm taking time to recover and exploring my options."</em> Punto. No amplíes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-cloud);">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">¿"What's your minimum to settle?"</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
          <em>"I'd rather hear M&S's position first before discussing specific figures."</em> Le tocan ellos mover.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-cloud);">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">¿"How long do you want this to take?"</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
          <em>"I'd prefer to resolve this as quickly as possible, but not at the cost of a fair outcome. I'm prepared to use the full conciliation period if needed."</em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-cloud);">
        <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">¿"Would you consider mediation/a meeting with M&S?"</p>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
          <em>"I'd prefer to keep this through you. I don't want direct contact with M&S at this stage."</em>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">Antes de colgar · checklist</h2>
    <div class="rounded-xl p-5" style="background: var(--color-primary-soft); border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2);">
      <ul class="text-sm space-y-2" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">
        <li>☐ Has apuntado <strong>su nombre completo</strong></li>
        <li>☐ Has apuntado <strong>su email directo</strong></li>
        <li>☐ Has apuntado <strong>su teléfono directo</strong> (no el switchboard)</li>
        <li>☐ Sabes <strong>cuándo va a contactar a M&S</strong></li>
        <li>☐ Has confirmado que <strong>la próxima comunicación será por email</strong></li>
        <li>☐ No has dado ninguna cifra</li>
        <li>☐ No has aceptado ninguna oferta en directo</li>
        <li>☐ No has mencionado tu nuevo trabajo</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs mt-3" style="color: var(--color-stone);">
      Cierre tipo: <em>"Thank you for the call. I'll wait to hear from you by email once you've spoken to M&S. Speak soon."</em>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-4" style="color: var(--color-graphite);">Inmediatamente después de colgar</h2>
    <div class="rounded-xl p-5" style="background: #fef3c7; border: 1px solid #fcd34d;">
      <ol class="text-sm space-y-2 list-decimal pl-5" style="color: #78350f;">
        <li><strong>Apúntalo todo</strong> mientras lo recuerdas: qué te preguntó, qué dijiste tú, qué dijo el conciliator sobre M&S, próximos pasos, fechas.</li>
        <li><strong>Pásamelo a mí o a Diego</strong>. No interpretes nada sola, lo procesamos juntos.</li>
        <li><strong>No respondas todavía</strong> a ningún email del conciliator que llegue después. Antes me lo enseñas.</li>
        <li><strong>No contactes a M&S por tu cuenta</strong>, ni siquiera para un detalle pequeño. Todo vía conciliator.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pb-12">
    <div class="rounded-xl p-5 text-center" style="background: var(--color-graphite); color: white;">
      <p class="text-sm mb-2 opacity-80">Recuerda</p>
      <p class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Estás en una posición fuerte.</p>
      <p class="text-sm opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
        Trece años de servicio. Una empresa que no puede producir un contrato firmado. Pattern claro de M-V durante más de tres años. Childcare disparity reconocida por la jurisprudencia.<br/>
        <strong>El tiempo juega a tu favor</strong>, no al de M&S.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</LightLayout>
